metadata.description:
Hello Bakers
Next to introduce is Pluto Dabtter!
üèõ An architect who designed and built the whole planet Dank. He comes from a family of architects, and after the death of his father, Pluto decided to take over the family business to honor his father. Damned mantises destroyed all the planet's architecture and buildings him and his family have been building over the years. After the invasion and seeing the consequences, he found some peace and calm in Wax (dab) and got addicted.
metadata.name: Architect Pluto Dabtter
